'''塞缪尔·弗雷德里克·“山姆”·史密斯'''（{{lang-en|Samuel Frederick "Sam" Smith}}，{{bd|1992年|5月19日}}），是一位[[英國|英國]]歌手及詞曲作家。他在2012年10月與[[解密兄弟|解密兄弟]]合作單曲〈{{link-en|Latch (歌曲)|Latch (song)|Latch}}〉而逐漸成名，這張單曲曾在[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]位居第11名。<ref name="UK chart">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/_/sam%20smith/|title=SAM SMITH|work=officialcharts.com|publisher=The Official UK Charts Company|accessdate=2014-05-18|archive-date=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627212340/http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/_/sam%20smith/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他之後在2013年5月與{{link-en|頑皮男孩|Naughty Boy}}合作發行的單曲〈{{link-en|La La La (頑皮男孩歌曲)|La La La (Naughty Boy song)|La La La}}〉更是登上排行榜第一名。<ref name="UK chart"/>

史密斯在2013年12月獲[[全英音樂獎|2014年全英音樂獎樂評人選擇獎]]和[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]的[[年度新声|2014年度新聲]]提名；<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25216850|title=Brits announce Critics' Choice 2014 shortlist|publisher=BBC|date=2013-12-05|accessdate=2013-12-19|archive-date=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151116051143/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25216850|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="so14">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01ky6g6/profiles/samsmith|title=Sound of 2014 Profile: Sam Smith|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2014-01-10|archive-date=2014-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228151148/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01ky6g6/profiles/samsmith|dead-url=no}}</ref>最後他也贏得了這兩個獎項。<ref name="BRIT">{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/brit-awards/10511427/Brits-Critics-Choice-Award-2014-Sam-Smith-announced-as-winner.html|title=Brits Critics' Choice Award 2014: Sam Smith announced as winner|publisher=The Telegraph|date=2013-12-12|accessdate=2013-12-19|archive-date=2014-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101215035/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/brit-awards/10511427/Brits-Critics-Choice-Award-2014-Sam-Smith-announced-as-winner.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25635440 |title=BBC Sound of 2014: Sam Smith |publisher=BBC |date=2014-01-10 |accessdate=2014-01-10 |archive-date=2016-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416083841/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25635440 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他計畫在2014年5月26日由[[Capitol唱片|Capitol唱片]]發行他的首張錄音室專輯《{{link-en|In the Lonely Hour|In the Lonely Hour}}》。<ref name="inthelonelyhour">{{cite web|url=http://www.factmag.com/2013/12/16/sam-smith-announces-debut-album-in-the-lonely-hour-shares-tour-dates/|title=Sam Smith announces debut album ''In the Lonely Hour'', shares tour dates|publisher=''Fact''|date=2013-12-16|accessdate=2013-12-19|archive-date=2016-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411021308/http://www.factmag.com/2013/12/16/sam-smith-announces-debut-album-in-the-lonely-hour-shares-tour-dates/|dead-url=no}}</ref>主打單曲〈{{link-en|Lay Me Down (山姆·史密斯歌曲)|Lay Me Down (Sam Smith song)|Lay Me Down}}〉在〈{{link-en|La La La (頑皮男孩歌曲)|La La La (Naughty Boy song)|La La La}}〉前先行發行。第二首單曲〈{{link-en|Money on My Mind|Money on My Mind}}〉也於2014年2月16日推出。<ref name="moneyonmymind">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/money-on-my-mind-ep/id775088328|title='Money On My Mind' - EP by Sam Smith|publisher=[[Itunes|Itunes]] (UK)|accessdate=2013-12-19|archive-date=2014-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141119111600/https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/money-on-my-mind-ep/id775088328|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年12月，史密斯获6个[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]提名，并赢得其中4个：[[格莱美奖最佳新人|最佳新人]]，凭借歌曲〈Stay with Me〉获得[[格莱美奖年度制作|年度制作]]，[[格莱美奖年度歌曲|年度歌曲]]，凭借专辑《{{link-en|In the Lonely Hour|In the Lonely Hour}}》获得{{link-en|格莱美奖最佳流行演唱专辑|Grammy Award for Best Pop Vocal Album|最佳流行演唱专辑}}。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-30345905 "Sam Smith nabs Grammy nominations"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-30345905 |date=20151016131201 }}. BBC. Retrieved 5 December 2014</ref>而在2016年，他則憑《[[007：惡魔四伏|007：惡魔四伏]]》的電影主題曲〈[[危機將至|危機將至]]〉獲得[[第73屆金球獎|第73屆金球獎]]的和[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡金像獎]]的「最佳原創歌曲獎」。2017年在環球音樂旗下廠牌Capitol唱片，發行专辑《[[痛快感受|痛快感受]]》睽違三年回歸主打〈{{le|擅長告別|Too Good at Goodbyes}}〉拿下生涯第6支英國金榜冠軍單曲。

==早年生活==
史密斯成長於[[英國|英國]][[劍橋郡|劍橋郡]]{{link-en|大奇斯丘|Great Chishill}}，<ref>{{cite news |last=Westbrook |first=Caroline |url=http://metro.co.uk/2014/01/10/who-is-sam-smith-five-fascinating-facts-about-the-bbcs-sound-of-2014-winner-4257529/ |title=Who is Sam Smith? Five fascinating facts about the BBC’s Sound of 2014 winner |work=metro.co.uk |publisher=METRO |date=2014-01-10 |accessdate=2014-05-19 |archive-date=2014-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517000608/http://metro.co.uk/2014/01/10/who-is-sam-smith-five-fascinating-facts-about-the-bbcs-sound-of-2014-winner-4257529/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在成名與畢業前於當地的一家店鋪工作。<ref name="contact"/>他曾就讀於[[彼索普斯托福|彼索普斯托福]]的{{link-en|聖瑪莉天主教學校 (彼索普斯托福)|St. Mary's Catholic School (Bishop's Stortford)|聖瑪莉天主教學校}}。<ref>{{cite news |last=Dearman |first=Natalie |url=http://www.hertsandessexobserver.co.uk/Whats-On-Leisure/Music/Former-Stortford-pupil-Sam-Smith-scores-UK-number-one-single-20130604165757.htm |title=Former Stortford pupil Sam Smith scores UK number one single |work=hertsandessexobserver.co.uk |publisher=Herts and Essex Newspapers Ltd |date=2013-06-04 |accessdate=2014-05-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218090806/http://www.hertsandessexobserver.co.uk/Whats-On-Leisure/Music/Former-Stortford-pupil-Sam-Smith-scores-UK-number-one-single-20130604165757.htm |archivedate=2013-12-18 }}</ref>史密斯是英國青年音樂劇團（Youth Music Theatre UK）的一員，並在2007年參與《Oh! Carol》演出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.youthmusictheatreuk.org/alumni|title=Alumni Youth Music Theatre UK|date=2013-12-17|accessdate=2014-05-19|archive-date=2014-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425224513/http://www.youthmusictheatreuk.org/alumni|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他花了數年在爵士歌手、鋼琴家{{link-en|喬安娜·伊登|Joanna Eden}}門下學習唱歌與寫歌。<ref name="contact">{{cite news |last=Miskiw |first=Sophie |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/article/sam-smith-brit-awards-lay-me-down_4080011 |title=Who Is BRIT Awards Winner Sam Smith? |work=contactmusic.com |publisher=Contactmusic.com Ltd |date=2014-02-24 |accessdate=2014-05-19 |archive-date=2014-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307025441/http://www.contactmusic.com/article/sam-smith-brit-awards-lay-me-down_4080011 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

史密斯的母親凱特·卡西迪（Kate Cassidy）是一位年收入超過50萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]的銀行家，她於2009年在高等法院與她的前雇主{{link-en|德利萬邦|Tullett Prebon}}展開150萬英鎊的訴訟。最終公司以她花太多時間在經營她兒子的音樂事業，而駁回了她的控告。<ref>{{cite news|first=Neil|last=Sears|first2=Ben|last2=Laurance|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1134509/City-banker-sacked-spending-company-time-sons-pop-dream.html|title=City banker is 'sacked for spending too much company time on son's pop dream'|work=dailymail.co.uk|publisher=Daily Mail|date=2009-02-02|accessdate=2014-05-19|archive-date=2014-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626105605/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1134509/City-banker-sacked-spending-company-time-sons-pop-dream.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/4445012/Banker-claims-she-was-sacked-for-promoting-sons-pop-career.html|title=Banker claims she was sacked for promoting son's pop career|work=telegraph.co.uk|publisher=The Telegraph|date=2009-02-03|accessdate=2014-05-19|archive-date=2014-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140329224231/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/4445012/Banker-claims-she-was-sacked-for-promoting-sons-pop-career.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

史密斯是歌手[[莉莉·艾倫|莉莉·艾倫]]和演員[[阿爾菲·阿倫|阿爾菲·阿倫]]的表弟。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nme.com/news/lily-allen/74818 |title=Nick Grimshaw and BBC Sound Of winner Sam Smith joke about Lily Allen's 'big mouth' |work=[[New_Musical_Express|New Musical Express]] |year=10 January 2014 |accessdate=2014-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042612/http://www.nme.com/news/lily-allen/74818 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==音樂生涯==
===2012－13年：突破===
史密斯在2012年10月與[[解密兄弟|解密兄弟]]合作單曲〈{{link-en|Latch (歌曲)|Latch (song)|Latch}}〉，這張單曲發行於2012年10月8日，並在[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]位居第11名。<ref name="UK chart"/>他在2013年2月發行首張單曲〈{{link-en|Lay Me Down (山姆·史密斯歌曲)|Lay Me Down (Sam Smith song)|Lay Me Down}}〉，這同時也是他首張專輯的主打單曲。接著在2013年5月與{{link-en|頑皮男孩|Naughty Boy}}合作單曲〈{{link-en|La La La (頑皮男孩歌曲)|La La La (Naughty Boy song)|La La La}}〉。這張單曲發行於2013年5月19日，並且爬上[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]首位。<ref name="UK chart"/>他也在是年夏季推出包含4首歌的[[迷你專輯|迷你專輯]]，第一首歌〈Stay  With Me〉由Two Inch Punch製作，並在2013年7月24日{{link-en|MistaJam|MistaJam}}的{{link-en|BBC Radio 1Xtra|BBC Radio 1Xtra}}節目上首次播出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crackintheroad.com/music/23303-new-sam-smith-safe-with-me/|title=New: Sam Smith - Safe With Me|publisher=Crack in the Road|date=2013-07-24|accessdate=2013-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006123254/http://www.crackintheroad.com/music/23303-new-sam-smith-safe-with-me|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>第二首歌〈Nirvana〉由Craze & Hoax和Jonathan Creek共同製作。這張迷你專輯也包含〈Latch〉的史密斯不插電獨唱版，還有〈I've Told You Now〉的現場演唱版。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/nirvana-ep/id708375165|title=iTunes - Music - Nirvana - EP by Sam Smith|publisher=iTunes|accessdate=2013-09-17|archive-date=2014-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027133213/https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/nirvana-ep/id708375165|dead-url=no}}</ref>史密斯也曾在2013年11月25日發行與解密兄弟、{{link-en|尼羅羅傑斯|Nile Rodgers}}和吉米·納普斯（Jimmy Napes）合作的〈Together〉，同時這也是《{{link-en|沉澱：混音精選|Settle: The Remixes}}》專輯中唯一的單曲。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/together-single/id761017155 |title=Together - Single |work=itunes.apple.com |publisher=[[iTunes|iTunes]] |accessdate=2014-05-19 |archive-date=2015-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150606025550/https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/together-single/id761017155 |dead-url=no }}</ref>史密斯獲得了[[全英音樂獎|2014年全英音樂獎樂評人選擇獎]]。<ref name="BRIT"/>

===2014－15年：《In the Lonely Hour》===
{{Main|In the Lonely Hour}}
史密斯首張專輯中的第二首單曲名為〈{{link-en|Money on My Mind|Money on My Mind}}〉，發行於2014年2月16日。史密斯在2014年3月29日首次登上美國電視節目《[[週六夜現場|週六夜現場]]》，<ref name="mtv">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1724912/meet-sam-smith-british-bartender-set-take-saturday-night-live-stage.jhtml|title=Meet Sam Smith: The British Bartender Set To Take The 'Saturday Night Live' Stage - MTV.com|work=[[MTV|MTV]]|last=Montgomery|first=James|date=2014-03-27|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-date=2014-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331102509/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1724912/meet-sam-smith-british-bartender-set-take-saturday-night-live-stage.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="vh1">{{cite web|url=http://www.vh1.com/music/tuner/2014-03-28/sam-smith-saturday-night-live|title=Get To Know Sam Smith Before He Plays Saturday Night Live - Music News + Gossip - VH1 Music|work=[[VH1|VH1]]|last=Exton|first=Emily|date=2014-03-28|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-date=2015-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510071205/http://www.vh1.com/music/tuner/2014-03-28/sam-smith-saturday-night-live/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="queerty">{{cite web|url=http://www.queerty.com/is-sam-smith-the-worlds-next-great-male-diva-20140327|title=Is Sam Smith The World’s Next Great Male Diva? / Queerty|work=Queerty|last=Tharrett|first=Matthew|date=2014-03-27|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304001742/http://www.queerty.com/is-sam-smith-the-worlds-next-great-male-diva-20140327|dead-url=no}}</ref>並演唱〈{{link-en|Stay with Me (山姆·史密斯歌曲)|Stay with Me (Sam Smith song)|Stay with Me}}〉和〈{{link-en|Lay Me Down (山姆·史密斯歌曲)|Lay Me Down (Sam Smith song)|Lay Me Down}}〉。據2013年12月16日的報導指出，史密斯的首張錄音室專輯《{{link-en|In the Lonely Hour|In the Lonely Hour}}》將由[[Capitol唱片|Capitol唱片]]於2014年5月26日發行。<ref name="inthelonelyhour"/>他形容這張專輯是「關於單戀」，因為他喜歡的人從來沒有對他表示過好感。<ref name="Sound of Boston">{{cite web|url=http://soundofboston.com/angel-cambridge-sam-smith/|title=The Angel of Cambridge: Sam Smith|work=Sound of Boston|last=Ollman|first=Jonah|date=2014-03-28|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-date=2018-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180604185242/http://soundofboston.com/angel-cambridge-sam-smith/|dead-url=no}}</ref>史密斯曾在[[圣潘克勒斯老教堂|圣潘克勒斯老教堂]]現場演唱這張專輯中的歌曲〈Lay Me Down〉，而這個現場演唱版本在[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]於2013年12月27日的促銷活動中提供免費下載。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.co.uk/Told-Live-Pancras-Church-London/dp/B00HG1ANVM|title=I've Told You Now (Live At St Pancras Old Church, London): Sam Smith|publisher=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]]|date=2013-12-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114051323/http://www.amazon.co.uk/Told-Live-Pancras-Church-London/dp/B00HG1ANVM|archivedate=2014-01-14}}</ref>而這張專輯中的〈Make It To Me〉是由解密兄弟的霍華德和吉米·納普斯共同作曲，並可以在[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]於2014年1月13日的促銷活動中免費下載。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/make-it-to-me-single/id785860884|title=iTunes - Music - Make It To Me - Single by Sam Smith|publisher=[[iTunes|iTunes]]|date=2014-01-13|accessdate=2014-05-19|archive-date=2014-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140602222427/https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/make-it-to-me-single/id785860884|dead-url=no}}</ref>史密斯在2014年夏季於美國舉行首次巡迴演出，並且主打新專輯中的歌曲。<ref name="Sound of Boston"/>2014年12月5日CBS的節目和葛萊美獎的官方Twitter中公布，山姆·史密斯入選六項提名。

2015年2月8日，山姆·史密斯在[[第57屆葛萊美獎|第57屆葛萊美獎]]中獲得包括「年度製作」〈Stay with Me (Darkchild Version)〉、「年度歌曲」〈Stay with Me (Darkchild Version)〉和「最佳新人」三個一般類獎項與流行類的「最佳流行演唱專輯」《In the Lonely Hour》在內的四項大獎，成為該屆的最大贏家。

===2016年：《危機將至》===
2016年1月10日，山姆·史密斯憑《[[007：惡魔四伏|007：惡魔四伏]]》所演唱的電影主題曲〈[[危機將至|危機將至]]〉獲得[[第73屆金球獎|第73屆金球獎]]的和[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡金像獎]]的「最佳原創歌曲獎」。

===2017－現今：《痛快感受》到疫情影響的《Love Goes》===
《痛快感受》創造了生涯另一首暢銷金曲〈Too Good At Goodbyes〉在全球數位串流突破10億次，《痛快感受》被滾石雜誌入選為2017最佳專輯之一。

2019年開始，山姆史密斯迎接全新自我形象，音樂曲風變換成時尚的輕電子舞曲，像是〈Dancing with a Stranger〉""、"〈How Do You Sleep?〉"、與[[黛咪·洛瓦托|黛咪·洛瓦托]]合唱〈I’m Ready〉在全球串流排行皆破億收聽，大受好評。不料原訂應在年中發行的全新大碟《To Die For》，卻遇上全球疫情影響延宕，最後終於宣布全新專輯名稱《愛的模樣》及企劃將在10月30號推出。

==個人生活==
史密斯表示他受到[[艾米·怀恩豪斯|艾米·怀恩豪斯]]影響，他也曾在2014年5月發出一則推特表示他仍然想念她。<ref name="4music">{{cite episode|title=This Week's Fresh Music|airdate=17 May 2014|network=[[4Music|4Music]]}}</ref>2014年5月，他在接受采访时公开[[出柜|出柜]]，表示自己是一名[[男同性恋|同性恋者]]，而《In the Lonely Hour》专辑的灵感便是来自自己单恋一个男人但是得不到回报的经历。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/05/28/sam-smith-gay_n_5404783.html|title=Sam Smith, British Singer, Comes Out|work=[[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]]|date=2014-05-28|accessdate=2014-05-29|archive-date=2014-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140529084646/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/05/28/sam-smith-gay_n_5404783.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他同时表示，希望把这变成一种“正常现象”，因为（身为同性恋）这件事本身就“不是什么问题”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/sam-smith-comes-out-gay-new-album-2014285|title=Sam Smith Comes Out as Gay, Wrote New Album For a Guy: "I Want to Make It a Normality"|work=US Magazine|date=2014-05-28|accessdate=2014-05-29|archive-date=2014-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140529103659/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/sam-smith-comes-out-gay-new-album-2014285|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年9月起與23歲美國男演員[[布蘭登·弗林|布蘭登·弗林]]（Brandon Flynn）交往<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/entertainment/a18229047/sam-smith-13-reasons-why-brandon-flynn-relationship-timeline/|last=Lewis|first=Anna|title=Sam Smith and Brandon Flynn: a relationship timeline|work=[[Cosmopolitan_(magazine)|Cosmopolitan]]|date=February 18, 2018|accessdate=March 1, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612140235/https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/entertainment/a18229047/sam-smith-13-reasons-why-brandon-flynn-relationship-timeline/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但已於2018年6月分手。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://pagesix.com/2018/06/27/sam-smith-and-brandon-flynn-split-after-nine-months/|title=Sam Smith and Brandon Flynn split after nine months|date=2018-06-27|work=Page Six|access-date=2018-06-28|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627204752/https://pagesix.com/2018/06/27/sam-smith-and-brandon-flynn-split-after-nine-months/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年10月，史密斯出柜表示其[[性别认同|认同]]为[[性别酷儿|性别酷儿]]，即非二元性别，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.towleroad.com/2017/10/sam-smith-genderqueer-feel-just-much-woman-man/|title=Sam Smith Comes Out as Genderqueer: 'I Feel Just as Much Woman as I am Man'|date=23 October 2017|publisher=|accessdate=2019-09-14|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605033420/http://www.towleroad.com/2017/10/sam-smith-genderqueer-feel-just-much-woman-man/|dead-url=no}}</ref>称自己身上“女性和男性的部分一样多”。<ref name="gender">{{cite web|url=http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/celebrity-life/sam-smith-i-feel-just-as-much-a-woman-as-i-am-man/news-story/1ffc1d95c5d053b246c89d80bd3887b5|title=Sam Smith: 'I feel just as much a woman as I am man'|website=news.com.au|accessdate=25 October 2017|5=|archive-date=2019-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190308083125/https://www.news.com.au/entertainment/celebrity-life/sam-smith-i-feel-just-as-much-a-woman-as-i-am-man/news-story/1ffc1d95c5d053b246c89d80bd3887b5|dead-url=no}}</ref>还坦言自己年轻时曾有一段时间“完全没有一件男装”，上学时也化全套浓妆。<ref name="NNN gq">{{cite web|url=http://www.newnownext.com/sam-smith-comes-out-as-gender-nonbinary/10/2017/|title=Sam Smith Comes Out As Gender-Nonbinary|last1=Voss|first1=Brandon|authorlink1=Brandon Voss|date=22 October 2017|website=www.newnownext.com|publisher=[[Logo_TV|Logo TV]]|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608111805/http://www.newnownext.com/sam-smith-comes-out-as-gender-nonbinary/10/2017/|archivedate=8 June 2019|accessdate=8 June 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://whatstrending.com/pop/24989-sam-smith-comes-out-as-gender-queer/|title=Sam Smith Comes Out As Gender Queer|date=23 October 2017|publisher=|accessdate=2019-09-14|archive-date=2019-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902042540/http://whatstrending.com/pop/24989-sam-smith-comes-out-as-gender-queer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年9月，史密斯表示自己认同的性别代词为性别中性的“[[单数they|they/them]]”，称自己“人生中一直抵触自己的性别，如今决定由内而外拥抱真实的自己”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-smith-asks-to-be-referred-to-as-they-instead-of-he-after-coming-out-as-gender-neutral-2547833 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2019-09-14 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913225209/https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-smith-asks-to-be-referred-to-as-they-instead-of-he-after-coming-out-as-gender-neutral-2547833 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Blackmom |first1=Michael |title=Sam Smith Announced That Their Gender Pronouns Are They/Them |url=https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/michaelblackmon/sam-smith-announced-that-their-preferred-gender-pronouns |website=BuzzfeedNews |accessdate=14 September 2019 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913215623/https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/michaelblackmon/sam-smith-announced-that-their-preferred-gender-pronouns |dead-url=no }}</ref>

